(function(skuid){
	var $ = skuid.$;
	$(document.body).one('pageload',function(){
		var userMappingModel = skuid.model.getModel('ComponenrUserTypeMapping');
		var userMapping = userMappingModel.getFirstRow();
        var userMappingShow= userMapping.Pop_Up_Greeting_Show__c;
		
		var eventSettingModel = skuid.model.getModel('EventSet');
		var eventSetting = eventSettingModel.getFirstRow();
        var Is_Show= eventSetting.Is_Pop_Up_Greeting__c;
		var greating= eventSetting.Pop_Up_Greeting__c;
		var eventId= eventSetting.Event_Edition__c;
		
		var modal = document.getElementById('myModal');
		var span = document.getElementsByClassName("grey-btn")[0];
		span.onclick = function() {modal.style.display = "none";}
		
		var modelA = skuid.model.getModel('EventSetting');
        var rowUser = modelA.getFirstRow();
        var bBC = rowUser.Button_colors__c;  //Button Background color (label)
        var bTC = rowUser.Button_Text_Color__c;
        $('.grey-btn').css('background',bBC);
        $('.grey-btn').css('color',bTC);
        
        var displayPopUp = true;
        
        var input = document.getElementById("sessionSpan");
    	var sessionId = input.innerHTML;
    	//console.log('sessionid: '+sessionId);
    	var sessionObj = {
    						SessionId : sessionId,
    						EventId   : eventId,
    						firstTime : false
    					};
    	
    	var localData = localStorage.getItem('SessionEventlogin');
    	if (localData) 
    	{ 
    	    sessionObj.firstTime = true;
    	    //console.log('localData ==  '+ localData);
    	    //console.log('sessionObj ==  '+ JSON.stringify(sessionObj));
    	    
    		var obj = JSON.parse(localData);
    		sessionObj.firstTime = true;
    		if(localData === JSON.stringify(sessionObj))
    		{
    			// No Display
    			displayPopUp = false;
    		}else
    		{
    			localStorage.removeItem('SessionEventlogin');  
    			sessionObj.firstTime = true;
    			localStorage.setItem('SessionEventlogin',JSON.stringify(sessionObj));
    			// Display
    			displayPopUp = true;
    		}
    		//console.log('localData ==  '+ localData);
    	}
    	else
    	{
    		sessionObj.firstTime = true;
    		localStorage.setItem('SessionEventlogin',JSON.stringify(sessionObj));
    		// Display
    		displayPopUp = true;
    	}		
      
		if(Is_Show !== true || userMappingShow !== true)
		{
		    //console.log('====1st')
		    modal.style.display = 'none';
	    }
	    else
	    {
	        if(displayPopUp == true)
	        {
	            //console.log('====TRrd')
	            modal.style.display = 'block';
	        }else
	        {
	            //console.log('====Flrd')
	            modal.style.display = 'none';
	        }
	    }
	});
})(skuid);
</script>
